<h2>Adventure Kids</h2>
<p class="highlight">Adventure Kids provides a fun, creative and safe place for kids to learn about the exciting life God has for them. Life in Christ is an adventure and a child&rsquo;s journey should be packed with fun and exploration. We are here to partner with parents to equip children to be passionate followers of Christ.</p>
